{"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/pullrequests/1710/comments/7259539.json"}, "code": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/osrf/gazebo/diff/osrf/gazebo:21c291a59116..1405d4359f9f?path=gazebo%2Fcommon%2FTime.hh"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/1710/_/diff#comment-7259539"}}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 1710, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/pullrequests/1710.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/1710"}}, "title": "Move FormatTime to Time class"}, "content": {"raw": "Using `int` as an input is a little confusing at first. I wonder if you could make it more readable with an enum:\n\n```\nenum FormatOption {DAYS = 0, HOURS = 1, MINUTES = 2, SECONDS = 3, MILLISECONDS = 4};\n\nstd::string FormattedString(FormatOption _start = 0, FormatOption _end = 4) const;\n```\n\nor something like that.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>Using <code>int</code> as an input is a little confusing at first. I wonder if you could make it more readable with an enum:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span><span class=\"nt\">enum</span> <span class=\"nt\">FormatOption</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"err\">DAYS</span> <span class=\"err\">=</span> <span class=\"err\">0,</span> <span class=\"err\">HOURS</span> <span class=\"err\">=</span> <span class=\"err\">1,</span> <span class=\"err\">MINUTES</span> <span class=\"err\">=</span> <span class=\"err\">2,</span> <span class=\"err\">SECONDS</span> <span class=\"err\">=</span> <span class=\"err\">3,</span> <span class=\"err\">MILLISECONDS</span> <span class=\"err\">=</span> <span class=\"err\">4</span><span class=\"p\">}</span><span class=\"o\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"nt\">std</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"nd\">string</span> <span class=\"nt\">FormattedString</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"nt\">FormatOption</span> <span class=\"nt\">_start</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"nt\">0</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"nt\">FormatOption</span> <span class=\"nt\">_end</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"nt\">4</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"nt\">const</span><span class=\"o\">;</span>\n</pre></div>\n\n\n<p>or something like that.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2015-06-02T21:57:37.175658+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Jackie K", "uuid": "{e3d60b62-b7c7-4863-b9b9-cdae9f123cec}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7Be3d60b62-b7c7-4863-b9b9-cdae9f123cec%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7Be3d60b62-b7c7-4863-b9b9-cdae9f123cec%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ea011fa2919d4bd4568b32b440eda779d=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsJK-0.png"}}, "nickname": "jacquelinekay", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:f56c822f-f75c-4665-80f9-6e7764893b9c"}, "inline": {"to": 101, "from": null, "outdated": true, "path": "gazebo/common/Time.hh"}, "updated_on": "2015-06-02T21:57:50.792112+00:00", "type": "pullrequest_comment", "id": 7259539}